[ProMED-mail seldom receives reports of dengue outbreaks in China. It would be of interest to know what the _Aedes aegypti_ situation is in Guangdong Province. The most recent dengue outbreak there reported by ProMED-mail (archive no. 20121022.1356841) was on 15 Oct 2012.

